    "LSTM can process long text, but the model can just acquire past information.",
    "BiLSTM allows getting more contextual information by using the two LSTMs, one taking the input in the forward direction and the other going in the backward direction of the given sequence [64].",
    "The final representation of the word concentrates on the left and right context making efficient use of previous and future features for a given time frame.",
